catList: Packet radio and networks, wireless local area networks and standards including IEEE 802.11 and ETSI/RES 10, enabling technologies with examples on FDMA, TDMA, CDMA,  FDD and TDD. First and second-generation mobile systems and associated networks (AMPS, ETACS, GSM, IS-54,IS-95. Third generation cellular systems. Mobility management in PCS/PCNs, multi-carrier wireless networks. Personal access communication systems (PACS), wireless ATM networks and satellite ATM networks.

Principles of air interface design, characteristics of the wireless medium, wireless medium access alternatives, wireless network planning and cellular design, mobility management, and applications in wireless wide area networks, including first and second- generation mobile systems and associated networks (GSM, IS-54,IS-95), third generation wireless network (W-CDMA), wireless local area networks (IEEE 802.11 HIPERLAN),wireless ad hoc networks.
